function myplot2(space,speed)
global ax2
plot(ax2,space,speed,'Marker',"*",'MarkerSize',3);
end
function myplot1(space,speed)
global ax1
plot(ax1,space,speed,'Marker',"*",'MarkerSize',3);
end
